---
import ElevationLayout from '../../layouts/ElevationLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/elevation/Hero.astro';
import Section from '../../components/elevation/Section.astro';

const specs = [
  {
    title: "Relational Fidelity Measurement",
    version: "0.1.0",
    status: "Draft",
    description: "Measuring whether AI agents maintain their declared identity across substrate changes, session boundaries, and operational pressure.",
    href: "/specs/relational-fidelity-measurement",
    date: "2026-04-05",
    schema: "/specs/relational-fidelity-measurement/v0.1/schema.json",
  },
];
---

<ElevationLayout
  title="Specifications"
  description="Open specifications for AI agent governance, identity fidelity, and trust architecture by Evoked."
>
  <Hero
    eyebrowParts={["Evoked", "Open Specifications", "Vol. 01"]}
    headline="The Specifications."
    sub="Most AI standards are closed by default. These are not. Open specifications for AI agent governance. Use them freely with attribution. All specifications published under Creative Commons CC BY 4.0."
  />

  <Section id="catalog" marker="FIG · I" label="Catalog" heading="Currently available.">
    <div class="specs-list">
      {specs.map((spec) => (
        <a href={spec.href} class="spec-card">
          <div class="spec-card-header">
            <h3>{spec.title}</h3>
            <div class="spec-card-meta">
              <span class="spec-card-version">v{spec.version}</span>
              <span class={`spec-card-status status-${spec.status.toLowerCase()}`}>{spec.status}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>{spec.description}</p>
          <div class="spec-card-footer">
            <time datetime={spec.date}>
              {new Date(spec.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
            </time>
            {spec.schema && <span class="spec-card-schema">JSON Schema</span>}
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section id="note" marker="NOTA · BENE" closing={true}>
    <div class="closing-body">
      <p>Specifications are the operational language of the Standard. Each one names what is measurable, what is verifiable, and what is not yet either.</p>
      <p>More specs land as the work clarifies. The directory is open. The schemas are inspectable. The methodology is ours; the format is permissive.</p>
      <div class="closing-ctas">
        <a class="cta cta-primary" href="/principles">Read the principles</a>
        <a class="cta cta-secondary" href="/patents">See the patents &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</ElevationLayout>

<style>
  .specs-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .spec-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 2.25rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 250, 240, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--el-rule);
    box-shadow: var(--el-panel-shadow);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--el-text);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }
  .spec-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--el-accent);
    background: rgba(255, 250, 240, 0.85);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .spec-card-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .spec-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--el-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--el-text);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .spec-card-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .spec-card-version {
    font-family: var(--el-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--el-accent-deep);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--el-rule);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .spec-card-status {
    font-family: var(--el-ui);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
  }
  .status-draft  { color: var(--el-accent); }
  .status-stable { color: var(--el-accent-deep); }

  .spec-card p {
    font-family: var(--el-body);
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--el-text-soft);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .spec-card-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--el-rule);
  }

  .spec-card-footer time {
    font-family: var(--el-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--el-text-quiet);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .spec-card-schema {
    font-family: var(--el-ui);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--el-accent);
  }

  .closing-body { max-width: 56ch; }
  .closing-body :global(p) {
    font-family: var(--el-body);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--el-text);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.005em;
  }
  .closing-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
